<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Link Kontrol Raporu</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;margin:0;padding:0;background:#f6f7fb;">
<div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px;">
    <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e7e9f1;border-radius:12px;padding:18px 18px 14px;">
        <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:18px;">Sistem Sağlığı · Broken Link Raporu</h2>
        <div style="color:#556070;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;">
            <div><strong>Base URL:</strong> {{base_url}}</div>
            <div><strong>Kontrol zamanı:</strong> {{checked_at}}</div>
            <div><strong>Özet:</strong> OK={{ok_count}} · BAD={{bad_count}} · Toplam={{total_count}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="height:12px;"></div>

    <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e7e9f1;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;">
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;">Hatalı Route Listesi (ilk 50)</h3>
        <div style="color:#556070;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;white-space:pre-wrap;">{{bad_list}}</div>
        <div style="margin-top:10px;color:#8a93a3;font-size:12px;">
            Not: Bu rapor admin paneldeki <em>Sistem Sağlığı → Linkleri kontrol et</em> butonundan otomatik oluşturulmuştur.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

